<topic id="applet_webapp_comparison">
  <title>Feature Matrix</title>
  <body>
    <p>The <ph keyref="authorComponent"/> was designed to provide the functionality of the standard
        <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> mode and can be embedded either in a third-party standalone
      Java application or customized as a Java Web Applet to provide WYSIWYG-like XML editing
      directly in your choice of web browsers.</p>
    <p>The Oxygen XML Web Author and Oxygen XML Web Author Component are re-implementations of the
        <ph keyref="product"/>
      <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol> mode user interface, based on JavaScript and HTML5. Its purpose
      is to enable XML editing and reviewing on your mobile devices and desktops, directly in a web
      browser environment. Since the interface was thinned down as much as possible, the core XML
      processing was moved into a Java-enabled server.</p>
